.SH FUNCTIONS
.LP
.B
\fBcheck(This, Item, [Option]) -> ok\fR
\fB               when\fR
\fB                   This :: wxCheckListBox(),\fR
\fB                   Item :: integer(),\fR
\fB                   Option :: {check, boolean()}.\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Checks the given item.

.PP
